":1780917485609},"bookId":"3ef2c972-dba1-4872-8b43-3b40b0f05f0c","deletedAt":1780917494426},{"id":"5c63e4c7-7587-48fb-83d6-23e0710d7f59","type":"mindMapCard","item":{"id":"bdc7ff65-6448-4cfe-98bc-b24749af9fff","title":"再怎么巧，我也不会直接砸到那个封印头上才对啊？所以说，洛溪应","content":"再怎么巧，我也不会直接砸到那个封印头上才对啊？所以说，洛溪应该还是有嫌疑的。","parentId":null,"children":[],"createdAt":1780917485609},"bookId":"3ef2c972-dba1-4872-8b43-3b40b0f05f0c","deletedAt":1780917494426},{"id":"eabad16c-e7ec-4a46-b9fa-007158c352ca","type":"mindMapCard","item":{"id":"9a2434b4-a815-4e41-a4b6-6c84e6b483e9","title":"那他是怎么犯案的呢？","content":"那他是怎么犯案的呢？","parentId":null,"children":[],"createdAt":1780917485610},"bookId":"3ef2c972-dba1-4872-8b43-3b40b0f05f0c","deletedAt":1780917494427},{"id":"7bfb1ceb-fb97-4800-9819-384db810d8dc","type":"mindMapCard","item":{"id":"16061cb1-4f74-4529-b8d3-2c02a1f726b1","title":"常佑思考到这一步时，大脑果断的宕机了。","content":"常佑思考到这一步时，大脑果断的宕机了。","parentId":null,"children":[],"createdAt":1780917485610},"bookId":"3ef2c972-dba1-4872-8b43-3b40b0f05f0c","deletedAt":1780917494427},{"id":"a438a18b-cdbb-448b-bdaf-418e4ee32a6a","type":"mindMapCard","item":{"id":"4a2bf0d5-b82a-4cfe-ab3d-9f05675e2940","title":"想不出来，嘿嘿。","content":"想不出来，嘿嘿。","parentId":null,"children":[],"createdAt":1780917485610},"bookId":"3ef2c972-dba1-4872-8b43-3b40b0f05f0c","deletedAt":1780917494428},{"id":"a62028d2-05a1-48ed-bac1-b17346bc6886","type":"mindMapCard","item":{"id":"2eb9eab4-1850-4aa9-941b-81050760a314","title":"她不是侦探，她擅长的领域不在这一块。","content":"她不是侦探，她擅长的领域不在这一块。","parentId":null,"children":[],"createdAt":1780917485610},"bookId":"3ef2c972-dba1-4872-8b43-3b40b0f05f0c","deletedAt":1780917494428},{"id":"b8daef0e-5fce-453a-8204-7b64a38ecdf8","type":"mindMapCard","item":{"id":"128cd24a-0b90-4186-8f7a-67bfdb37e358","title":"“缘舜，你说那洛溪竟然能引来天火，还精准的把那封印给破了，那","content":"“缘舜，你说那洛溪竟然能引来天火，还精准的把那封印给破了，那你倒是再讲讲，他怎么不干脆把天火直接往我们脑袋上砸，给我们统统灭了，再拿个火把，去给封印点了啊？若是他真有那么大能耐，又这么念旧情，恐怕你我二人，包括当初参与围剿的各位，是不能坐在这打嘴仗啊。”","parentId":null,"children":[],"createdAt":1780917485610},"boo