候，常佑终于愿意分一些注意力给","content":"吃了个半饱，开始扒拉酒盖子的时候，常佑终于愿意分一些注意力给旁边的青妙音：“你怎么一直看着我？”","parentId":null,"children":[],"createdAt":1780917485620},"bookId":"3ef2c972-dba1-4872-8b43-3b40b0f05f0c","deletedAt":1780917494509},{"id":"3e9dd2c9-9136-4d93-8ba2-f7aca6b15afd","type":"mindMapCard","item":{"id":"fac280b1-74f4-404f-a6a1-1bbe92ce8376","title":"“林前辈让我等你吃完。我待会要带你去找个睡觉的地方。”","content":"“林前辈让我等你吃完。我待会要带你去找个睡觉的地方。”","parentId":null,"children":[],"createdAt":1780917485620},"bookId":"3ef2c972-dba1-4872-8b43-3b40b0f05f0c","deletedAt":1780917494509},{"id":"587b911c-3a44-40f8-a799-ec5f98b2882a","type":"mindMapCard","item":{"id":"58e3f8e6-b98d-4f26-82ee-f11360ea3b8b","title":"“哦，那你饿了吗？”","content":"“哦，那你饿了吗？”","parentId":null,"children":[],"createdAt":1780917485620},"bookId":"3ef2c972-dba1-4872-8b43-3b40b0f05f0c","deletedAt":1780917494509},{"id":"ea30af43-7441-40c1-a02e-0636bf634f75","type":"mindMapCard","item":{"id":"d2912fa4-68b9-4b46-985e-bc22ba1cb85d","title":"常佑舔了舔自己的爪子，上边还有些酒香味，混着木头盖子的味道。","content":"常佑舔了舔自己的爪子，上边还有些酒香味，混着木头盖子的味道。","parentId":null,"children":[],"createdAt":1780917485620},"bookId":"3ef2c972-dba1-4872-8b43-3b40b0f05f0c","deletedAt":1780917494509},{"id":"911fe9ac-e127-467d-acba-6affd7998092","type":"mindMapCard","item":{"id":"70ac347d-83b1-454d-aac5-7cda1faf07bd","title":"青妙音犹豫道：“有一点吧。”","content":"青妙音犹豫道：“有一点吧。”","parentId":null,"children":[],"createdAt":1780917485620},"bookId":"3ef2c972-dba1-4872-8b43-3b40b0f05f0c","deletedAt":1780917494509},{"id":"45806aed-75ab-4f78-9612-461c083a0564","type":"mindMapCard","item":{"id":"2cdeec30-5650-4c62-8ba2-14f3ed3c343f","title":"她还是没办法把面前这个看起来毫无攻击力的小狗，和刚刚那个看起","content":"她还是没办法把面前这个看起来毫无攻击力的小狗，和刚刚那个看起来就非常强的大妖关联起来。","parentId":null,"children":[],"createdAt":1780917485620},"bookId":"3ef2c972-dba1-4872-8b43-3b40b0f05f0c","deletedAt":1780917494509},{"id":"dadceca2-556e-4ddd-ba3e-0d76c7e0a2ee","type":"mindMapCard","item":{"id":"698ab4ff-78d4-4ea4-9e09-cf3601ae8053","title":"“那，你想吃什么就自己拿，我喝点酒。”","content":"“那，你想吃什么就自己拿，我喝点酒。”","pare