6170713703","type":"mindMapCard","item":{"id":"f770e521-f109-42f4-bcaa-38d098719f03","title":"“是吗，那太好了。天火一事有解，大妖一事也有解，一切还就拜托","content":"“是吗，那太好了。天火一事有解，大妖一事也有解，一切还就拜托您了。”","parentId":null,"children":[],"createdAt":1780917485621},"bookId":"3ef2c972-dba1-4872-8b43-3b40b0f05f0c","deletedAt":1780917494526},{"id":"76df3597-a989-499b-8232-f5641725a3e0","type":"mindMapCard","item":{"id":"3ff8f8f1-b234-41a8-936e-cb4dbc6c4388","title":"李继作揖道谢。","content":"李继作揖道谢。","parentId":null,"children":[],"createdAt":1780917485621},"bookId":"3ef2c972-dba1-4872-8b43-3b40b0f05f0c","deletedAt":1780917494526},{"id":"7a61c39d-edb7-4879-91b7-428053001254","type":"mindMapCard","item":{"id":"d0c91ec3-0e1e-4881-939e-df2b16d9d1b5","title":"“哎呀，搞这套...”","content":"“哎呀，搞这套...”","parentId":null,"children":[],"createdAt":1780917485621},"bookId":"3ef2c972-dba1-4872-8b43-3b40b0f05f0c","deletedAt":1780917494527},{"id":"2968bcfd-40d1-4dab-a890-df5a6063592e","type":"mindMapCard","item":{"id":"54fa2477-3303-467d-bd7c-e91c944b23fb","title":"常佑在天庭可没被人这样正儿八经的对待过。她扭了扭头，转过身去","content":"常佑在天庭可没被人这样正儿八经的对待过。她扭了扭头，转过身去，又回头看他们一眼。做出一副不太适应的样子。实际上心里可得意。","parentId":null,"children":[],"createdAt":1780917485621},"bookId":"3ef2c972-dba1-4872-8b43-3b40b0f05f0c","deletedAt":1780917494527},{"id":"ae7901a9-81e8-4bec-aafc-b1077f1c254d","type":"mindMapCard","item":{"id":"48b6bfa8-b61e-4140-94a5-4efde9919b6f","title":"她想了一下那些人都啥嘴脸，要么就是不把自个当个有脑子的看，要","content":"她想了一下那些人都啥嘴脸，要么就是不把自个当个有脑子的看，要么就是无视她，要么呢，就是给她特殊对待——看在烂柯的份上。她在上边过得可憋屈，打得过的惹不起，惹得起的不敢打，每天就那么点娱乐活动还要被限制。哼，这下来还真就下来对了，你看，这有人鞠躬，有人端茶的，她扭头看了看青妙音，还有上菜的！","parentId":null,"children":[],"createdAt":1780917485621},"bookId":"3ef2c972-dba1-4872-8b43-3b40b0f05f0c","deletedAt":1780917494527},{"id":"2784de3f-d56b-4599-a6d0-dc7949866516","type":"mindMapCard","item":{"id":"0952e792-d1d1-4e9b-9c02-00fb48192473","title":"“既然如此，常前辈是要即刻启程，还是先在此休整一番，明日启程","content":"“既然如此，常前辈是要即刻启程，还是先在此休整一番，明日启程？”","parentId":null,"children":[],"createdAt":1780917485621},"bookId":"3ef2c972-dba1-4872-8b43-3b40b0f05f0c","deletedAt":1780917494527},{"id":"400c2143-4371-4e68-ae86-5c8dd6a278e9","type":"mindMapCard","item":{"id":"aa28b523-d239-4b0b-bd31-88d57f171fe9","title":"李继装作没看见常佑的小动作，继续问。","content":"李继装作没看见常佑的小动作，继续问。","parentId":null,"children":[],"createdAt":1780917485621},"bookId":"3ef2c972-dba1-4872-8b43-3b40b0f05f0c","deletedAt":1780917494527},{"id":"8ddc80e8-f8fb-446c-81aa-ceb0d5aab866","type":"mindMapCard","item":{"id":"1391c770-ef48-4094-a979-6be816a09049","title":"林九霄肩膀抖动，用手挡着脸，身体不自然的倾向一旁。他在憋笑，","content":"林九霄肩膀抖动，用手挡着脸，身体不自然的倾向一旁。他在憋笑，似乎想到了什么开心的事情。","parentId":null,"children":[],"createdAt":1780917485621},"bookId":"3ef2c972-dba1-4872-8b43-3b40b0f05f0c","deletedAt":1780917494527},{"id":"8a730cbd-87ca-44d3-bb7e-008b23f1f27b","type":"mindMapCard","item":{"id":"b538ed7f-e05c-4bb9-bab1-f42f3ee0f7b7","title":"“当然是睡..诶不是，我要即刻启程！那个什么乾镇在哪？”","content":"“当然是睡..诶不是，我要即刻启程！那个什么乾镇在哪？”","parentId":null,"children":[],"createdAt":1780917485621},"bookId":"3ef2c972-dba1-4872-8b43-3b40b0f05f0c","deletedAt":1780917494527},{"id":"58350a42-59c4-40bb-bc9b-f14f0b617452","type":"mindMapCard","item":{"id":"b4726e54-27db-43cd-9920-8d793f5e70b0","title":"常佑扭头，一股熟悉的“场”正在往这里迫近，她再次化为人身，脸","content":"常佑扭头，一股熟悉的“场”正在往这里迫近，她再次化为人身，脸上有着遮掩不住的焦急。","parentId":null,"children":[],"createdAt":1780917485621},"bookId":"3ef2c972-dba1-4872-8b43-3b40b0f05f0c","deletedAt":1780917494527},{"id":"f189591e-cb45-4b4f-9b85-88e308c5416b","type":"mindMapCard","item":{"id":"f3e74499-6947-4df6-a4bb-a91228f7f1c3","title":"我去，来真的？","content":"我去，来真的？","parentId":null,"children":[],"createdAt":1780917485621},"bookId":"3ef2c972-dba1-4872-8b43-3b40b0f05f0c","deletedAt":1780917494527},{"id":"08d92706-9dd3-48e5-9bd2-8bb31179086d","type":"mindMapCard","item":{"id":"780e2e79-a686-4302-a239-ad1d22ef9cf3","title":"云生慈下来解决？不是烂柯？虽然我有点期待吧，但是！","content":"云生慈下来解决？不是烂柯？虽然我有点期待吧，但是！","parentId":null,"children":[],"createdAt":1780917485621},"bookId":"3ef2c972-dba1-4872-8b43-3b40b0f05f0c","deletedAt":1780917494527},{"id":"a6633ce0-1054-4acb-a01c-eca4f5b1625c","type":"mindMapCard","item":{"id":"d6d0687e-8948-4b4b-b208-330ccb54a3ea","title":"刚吵完架的人是要装不熟还是装没看见他啊，在线等急...啊不对","content":"刚吵完架的人是要装不熟还是装没看见他啊，在线等急...啊不对我还是先跑路吧！","parentId":null,"children":[],"createdAt":1780917485621},"bookId":"3ef2c972-dba1-4872-8b43-3b40b0f05f0c","deletedAt":1780917494527},{"id":"98aca0db-f3f2-4d19-a829-21ed3d41f44a","type":"mindMapCard","item":{"id":"7f0715e7-83f6-4fa5-8cdb-e07a13cc3334","title":"李继拿出寻路盘，丢给常佑：“只要你心想着乾镇，这法宝便会带你","content":"李继拿出寻路盘，丢给常佑：“只要你心想着乾镇，这法宝便会带你去。”","parentId":null,"children":[],"createdAt":1780917485621},"bookId":"3ef2c972-dba1-4872-8b43-3b40b0f05f0c","deletedAt":1780917494527},{"id":"565bae20-3a27-4c70-8fea-0f3f8bda04be","type":"mindMapCard","item":{"id":"f0f03c34-8c5d-4ed9-998b-ee43d44ed7c3","title":"“这么好的东西你早不给我！”","content":"“这么好的东西你早不给我！”","parentId":null,"children":[],"createdAt":1780917485622},"bookId":"3ef2c972-dba1-4872-8b43-3b40b0f05f0c","deletedAt":1780917494528},{"id":"5a598f6d-a31d-4245-a13f-2cbe5b592c54","type":"mindMapCard","item":{"id":"b235deb7-9874-40d0-b53d-9561b32c36a9","title":"常佑拿了寻路盘，拔腿就跑到了门口，肉眼都能穿过云层，看见人间","content":"常佑拿了寻路盘，拔腿就跑到了门口，肉眼都能穿过云层，看见人间了。然而还是晚了一步，那人已经到了面前。丝丝缕缕的线落下，眼看着就要把她缠绕。常佑哇哇大叫，这玩意她再也不想体验了！","parentId":null,"children":[],"createdAt":1780917485622},"bookId":"3ef2c972-dba1-4872-8b43-3b40b0f05f0c","deletedAt":1780917494528},{"id":"4aee5ded-2d96-4f3d-9952-c3f735a71d94","type":"mindMapCard","item":{"id":"33087f65-2968-4878-8b13-cf7406963f2e","title":"她有一次跑出去，到神仙们的宴会上玩，云生慈来寻人，为了不被他","content":"她有一次跑出去，到神仙们的宴会上玩，云生慈来寻人，为了不被他发现，常佑特意躲在桌子底下，他要来，她就跑到另外一个桌子下去，那些神仙都忙着喝酒寻乐，懒得理桌下是否藏着一个小妖。","parentId":null,"children":[],"createdAt":1780917485622},"bookId":"3ef2c972-dba1-4872-8b43-3b40b0f05f0c","deletedAt":1780917494528},{"id":"e4539364-7d03-48b1-96b5-024ebb38ad13","type":"mindMapCard","item":{"id":"8e91d5bc-9e33-4f68-9979-1e93bfe4d234","title":"而另外一头，云生慈彻底恼了，他拿出从烂柯那借来的法宝——寻踪","content":"而另外一头，云生慈彻底恼了，他拿出从烂柯那借来的法宝——寻踪丝，它循着常佑的妖气，将她五花大绑，直接裹成了大粽子。事后，云生慈冷着脸拿剪刀给她剪了老久，把她的毛都要剪秃了，对于一个妖来说，失去自己的毛是多么的坏，云生慈这个人一点也不能体会！","parentId":null,"children":[],"createdAt":1780917485622},"bookId":"3ef2c972-dba1-4872-8b43-3b40b0f05f0c","deletedAt":1780917494528},{"id":"3b9acad3-c75f-4ba2-b31a-68682c010e32","type":"mindMapCard","item":{"id":"32d07a4c-e69b-4ba3-8545-c396550002cb","title":"为了让云生慈也体会到失去毛的滋味，常佑换位思考，把他的衣服咬","content":"为了让云生慈也体会到失去毛的滋味，常佑换位思考，把他的衣服咬的这里一个洞，那里一个洞。","parentId":null,"children":[],"createdAt":1780917485622},"bookId":"3ef2c972-dba1-4872-8b43-3b40b0f05f0c","deletedAt":1780917494528},{"id":"d8728969-f300-4346-90b5-8a1ca2c2b349","type":"mindMapCard","item":{"id":"712e88eb-57f1-4eae-836d-fd3c44bb2a8d","title":"……效果不太好！根本没人觉得他在出糗，反而认为这是他勤俭持家","content":"……效果不太好！根本没人觉得他在出糗，反而认为这是他勤俭持家。","parentId":null,"children":[],"createdAt":1780917485622},"bookId":"3ef2c972-dba1-4872-8b43-3b40b0f05f0c","deletedAt":1780917494528},{"id":"66bf7dfc-ea29-4db9-8601-8ed9e96f47b9","type":"mindMapCard","item":{"id":"15a2eb6b-a978-42dd-9cca-5009eab80821","title":"在寻踪丝即将接触到自己皮肤那一刻，天火燃烧起来，常佑的耳朵再","content":"在寻踪丝即将接触到自己皮肤那一刻，天火燃烧起来，常佑的耳朵再次冒出，她丝毫没注意到，跟在她身后的李继和林九霄见到这情形，都各自祭出武器。李继的长剑再次现行，而林九霄也拿出了自己的铁扇。","parentId":null,"children":[],"createdAt":1780917485622},"bookId":"3ef2c972-dba1-4872-8b43-3b40b0f05f0c","deletedAt":1780917494528},{"id":"7ed40e4b-f8e3-4e83-b110-7e9a94393af7","type":"mindMapCard","item":{"id":"b2148637-ee99-4d28-ad85-da57d5cc2337","title":"他们都很紧张，紧张于不知后面是否还会有第二次战斗，来者是敌是","content":"他们都很紧张，紧张于不知后面是否还���有第���次战斗，���者是敌是���？看见常佑身上燃起天火，更是心提到了嗓子眼。","parentId":null,"children":[],"createdAt":1780917485622},"bookId":"3ef2c972-dba1-4872-8b43-3b40b0f05f0c","deletedAt":1780917494528},{"id":"d526cfb3-dedf-4c9c-ab84-ee36a5b29f4f","type":"mindMapCard","item":{"id":"a20bd290-00f8-4aa8-b71a-cba04358caea","title":"那从天上降下的人身着白色外袍，上缀金丝，辅以红色异兽纹，底衫","content":"那从天上降下的人身着白色外袍，上缀金丝，辅以红色异兽纹，底衫同样为白，腰间挂着龙头玉佩。一手持瓶，一手牵着寻踪丝。","parentId":null,"children":[],"createdAt":1780917485622},"bookId":"3ef2c972-dba1-4872-8b43-3b40b0f05f0c","deletedAt":1780917494528},{"id":"7ef916b6-c563-42a5-984a-4e6420abefc6","type":"mindMapCard","item":{"id":"7611b421-0707-477c-87f7-53f528c9d24f","title":"是云生慈。","content":"是云生慈。","parentId":null,"children":[],"createdAt":1780917485622},"bookId":"3ef2c972-dba1-4872-8b43-3b40b0f05f0c","deletedAt":1780917494528},{"id":"fa90ee70-bd10-4135-a4f8-8f8c468e4054","type":"mindMapCard","item":{"id":"d4c155bd-8f83-446b-9bc8-eb84cf712ecb","title":"“常佑，你又要去哪？”","content":"“常佑，你又要去哪？”","parentId":null,"children":[],"createdAt":1780917485622},"bookId":"3ef2c972-dba1-4872-8b43-3b40b0f05f0c","deletedAt":1780917494528},{"id":"18f45ee9-5ff6-4f21-8aca-18824029da07","type":"mindMapCard","item":{"id":"3cb24aa9-a343-46ec-a861-f28d39445f97","title":"“我去帮人！你别拦着我，快把这些东西收回去啊。”","content":"“我去帮人！你别拦着我，快把这些东西收��去啊。”","parentId":null,"children":[],"createdAt":1780917485622},"bookId":"3ef2c972-dba1-4872-8b43-3b40b0f05f0c","deletedAt":1780917494528},{"id":"b4fee9e1-8ffa-43f5-a470-95d4e2024f70","type":"mindMapCard","item":{"id":"fa726563-ff22-4c5b-a662-b5c703dcf572","title":"“帮什么？”","content":"“帮什么？”","parentId":null,"children":[],"createdAt":1780917485622},"bookId":"3ef2c972-dba1-4872-8b43-3b40b0f05f0c","deletedAt":1780917494528},{"id":"f87c7be3-6e95-48d4-b08c-41d0aec61041","type":"mindMapCard","item":{"id":"337769d4-6baa-4446-924a-27244f117592","title":"话音刚落，云生慈已经来到常佑身旁，他伸手，抓住了常佑的右手腕","content":"话音刚落，云生慈已经来到常佑身旁，他伸手，抓住了常佑的右手腕，阻止她下一步的动作——掏刀。","parentId":null,"children":[],"createdAt":1780917485622},"bookId":"3ef2c972-dba1-4872-8b43-3b40b0f05f0c","deletedAt":1780917494528},{"id":"b5038e92-a289-43aa-94e9-c8d2353e9394","type":"mindMapCard","item":{"id":"20989f8a-339f-466f-b80a-5423a2446001","title":"常佑朝他呲牙。","content":"常佑朝他呲牙。","parentId":null,"children":[],"createdAt":1780917485622},"bookId":"3ef2c972-dba1-4872-8b43-3b40b0f05f0c","deletedAt":1780917494528},{"id":"16370bd0-483e-4f4e-93a6-6939c11cee80","type":"mindMapCard","item":{"id":"67b7ef57-80ae-4ffe-b04c-95bd5ea13d5c","title":"要打，等事情结束。他在常佑耳侧轻轻说。常佑对云生慈凑这么近说","content":"要打，等事情结束。他在常佑耳侧轻轻说。常佑对云生慈凑这么近说话这事，感到十分的不适应，一般来说，他俩凑那么近，一般是打起来了。她的身体重心有意识地往另外一侧倾，似乎巴不得下一秒就消失在他视野里。","parentId":null,"children":[],"createdAt":1780917485622},"bookId":"3ef2c972-dba1-4872-8b43-3b40b0f05f0c","deletedAt":1780917494528},{"id":"2c59bd64-6d0b-4067-bc00-b4517381f6f8","type":"mindMapCard","item":{"id":"fec70171-5116-4c21-acf9-dbadb7098c2f","title":"李继缩地成寸，来到云生慈面前，作揖，而后发问：“敢问常前辈，","content":"李继缩地成寸，来到云生慈面前，作揖，而后发问：“敢问常前辈，这位是？”","parentId":null,"children":[],"createdAt":1780917485622},"bookId":"3ef2c972-dba1-4872-8b43-3b40b0f05f0c","deletedAt":1780917494528},{"id":"edd812eb-11f1-4b75-8f99-6f4395fd5535","type":"mindMapCard","item":{"id":"6dee4e95-d51a-48da-9e55-196c2ea44f12","title":"“他嘛，他就是你们想要的人啦，来灭天火的...”","content":"“他嘛，他就是你们想要的人啦，来灭天火的...”","parentId":null,"children":[],"createdAt":1780917485622},"bookId":"3ef2c972-dba1-4872-8b43-3b40b0f05f0c","deletedAt":1780917494528},{"id":"9f9cb531-a498-46ad-86f1-35efd5e3a1a8","type":"mindMapCard","item":{"id":"436daa03-4bf5-4c67-a4ab-a9198f1aed78","title":"常佑满脸的不情愿。让我来介绍他，哎呀，感觉太奇怪了。他在天上","content":"常佑满脸的不情愿。让我来介绍他，哎呀，感觉太奇怪了。他在天上可有名呢，都轮不着我介绍，次次都是他介绍我，哼。","parentId":null,"children":[],"createdAt":1780917485622},"bookId":"3ef2c972-dba1-4872-8b43-3b40b0f05f0c","deletedAt":1780917494529},{"id":"781619ce-fe87-4f17-ae4b-26c0eefca254","type":"mindMapCard","item":{"id":"76f810f8-a9c3-43f2-bfec-3e12c7948c3e","title":"“啊！这位仙长，敢问贵姓？”","content":"“啊！这位仙长，敢问贵姓？”","parentId":null,"children":[],"createdAt":1780917485622},"bookId":"3ef2c972-dba1-4872-8b43-3b40b0f05f0c","deletedAt":1780917494529},{"id":"2deefbce-b70b-462a-8757-ef4a9d7fca6a","type":"mindMapCard","item":{"id":"5cbd911f-a8a4-4d33-ae63-edda5e53d380","title":"林九霄扮演着捧哏的角色，立刻接上话。","content":"林九霄扮演着捧哏的角色，立刻接上话。","parentId":null,"children":[],"createdAt":1780917485622},"bookId":"3ef2c972-dba1-4872-8b43-3b40b0f05f0c","deletedAt":1780917494529},{"id":"7e97557d-908d-4c38-a5fd-b1e930a8deee","type":"mindMapCard","item":{"id":"bdd37ab4-6d00-42fb-b098-40a4f5cb56a9","title":"“我并无仙职，免贵姓云，云生慈。生生不息的生，慈悲的慈。”","content":"“我并无仙职，免贵姓云，云生慈。生生不息的生，慈悲的慈。”","parentId":null,"children":[],"createdAt":1780917485622},"bookId":"3ef2c972-dba1-4872-8b43-3b40b0f05f0c","deletedAt":1780917494529},{"id":"b5408df0-398f-4c05-94f8-60494e066b0a","type":"mindMapCard","item":{"id":"266fa942-c7c3-4f73-82ce-a6ee56471f01","title":"“是云前辈。既然人终于来了，那我也不绕圈子，事态实在紧急。天","content":"“是云前辈。既然人终于来了，那我也不绕圈子，事态实在紧急。天火一事，待如何解决？”","parentId":null,"children":[],"createdAt":1780917485622},"bookId":"3ef2c972-dba1-4872-8b43-3b40b0f05f0c","deletedAt":1780917494529},{"id":"de260a6c-3db2-4b96-894f-198292ccb4e7","type":"mindMapCard","item":{"id":"485d4412-0fc3-4f1e-8546-9d4038acfa4d","title":"林九霄神情严肃。","content":"林九霄神情严肃。","parentId":null,"children":[],"createdAt":1780917485623},"bookId":"3ef2c972-dba1-4872-8b43-3b40b0f05f0c","deletedAt":1780917494529},{"id":"3f575f81-3453-4668-a199-05dfe1d0810c","type":"mindMapCard","item":{"id":"6b4ec110-436e-42bf-ba18-c21e8c2b209a","title":"“这是濯莲水。”","content":"“这是濯莲水。”","parentId":null,"children":[],"createdAt":1780917485623},"bookId":"3ef2c972-dba1-4872-8b43-3b40b0f05f0c","deletedAt":1780917494529},{"id":"0be8ecad-7fe7-4583-94e5-7cef5213526e","type":"mindMapCard","item":{"id":"4de4adc4-675a-41a8-92d8-ca0d1671c6d1","title":"云生慈将手中瓷瓶递出，这瓷瓶不大不小，周围白雾萦绕，瓶身画的","content":"云生慈将手中瓷瓶递出，这瓷瓶不大不小，周围白雾萦绕，瓶身画的是一幅蟠桃图。","parentId":null,"children":[],"createdAt":1780917485623},"bookId":"3ef2c972-dba1-4872-8b43-3b40b0f05f0c","deletedAt":1780917494529},{"id":"00c4da90-9b4c-414c-824d-14996bf35227","type":"mindMapCard","item":{"id":"27f2b216-6d7b-4a21-a647-5d0e6329266e","title":"“以濯莲水做祭品，开坛祈雨，自有仙人将天火解决。莫怪我来晚，","content":"“以濯莲水做祭品，开坛祈雨，自有仙人将天火解决。莫怪我来晚，事情繁琐，需得一步一步解决。”","parentId":null,"children":[],"createdAt":1780917485623},"bookId":"3ef2c972-dba1-4872-8b43-3b40b0f05f0c","deletedAt":1780917494529},{"id":"aacb57a7-dfce-4930-9b68-1cd363da8d89","type":"mindMapCard","item":{"id":"5174aec3-eac2-42d9-85bb-48c3ce3f6d9f","title":"虽然面对着李继二人，然而云生慈的注意力还是大多数放在一旁的常","content":"虽然面对着李继二人，然而云生慈的注意力还是大多数放在一旁的常佑身上，常佑正在和他暗暗较劲，手上的力气一点点加大，那天火还在她的皮肤上跳动着，虽然常佑有意控制不让它烧到自己身上，但她想打人的心一点也没藏。","parentId":null,"children":[],"createdAt":1780917485623},"bookId":"3ef2c972-dba1-4872-8b43-3b40b0f05f0c","deletedAt":1780917494529},{"id":"a9bf1344-bab0-46ee-afe1-c244b9dab667","type":"mindMapCard","item":{"id":"5f8ffc38-3a64-47a4-82f3-25677b8cf9e4","title":"“多谢云前辈！”","content":"“多谢云前辈！”","parentId":null,"children":[],"createdAt":1780917485623},"bookId":"3ef2c972-dba1-4872-8b43-3b40b0f05f0c","deletedAt":1780917494529},{"id":"126824c6-1ee3-45b5-a02b-6908acc1419f","type":"mindMapCard","item":{"id":"bda5afd3-6454-403e-bac3-f127fde16a5e","title":"李继连连道谢：“先前是我们冒犯常前辈了。”","content":"李继连连道谢：“先前是我们冒犯常前辈了。”","parentId":null,"children":[],"createdAt":1780917485623},"bookId":"3ef2c972-dba1-4872-8b43-3b40b0f05f0c","deletedAt":1780917494529},{"id":"49842d4a-46d1-4714-b741-78e1d887d8d2","type":"mindMapCard","item":{"id":"39c06418-e224-4ab1-ac80-5dfe29e1bf09","title":"林九霄也面露喜色。而后像是哆啦a梦一样从芥子袋里掏出一件法宝","content":"林九霄也面露喜色。而后像是哆啦a梦一样从芥子袋里掏出一件法宝，形似一面镜子，递给云生慈。","parentId":null,"children":[],"createdAt":1780917485623},"bookId":"3ef2c972-dba1-4872-8b43-3b40b0f05f0c","deletedAt":1780917494529},{"id":"62d0cab6-b692-4620-ae9d-bf5af46f0c48","type":"mindMapCard","item":{"id":"f333a5fa-50db-4a0a-baf6-57b2be01ec2c","title":"“此物名叫原镜，乃是我在外游历之际所获，将灵力灌入其中，可破","content":"“此物名叫原镜，乃是我在外游历之际所获，将灵力灌入其中，可破迷障，见本心。一些心意，还请云前辈收下。”","parentId":null,"children":[],"createdAt":1780917485623},"bookId":"3ef2c972-dba1-4872-8b43-3b40b0f05f0c","deletedAt":1780917494529},{"id":"53246bd1-f29d-44a7-a71b-f6d21b9104d7","type":"mindMapCard","item":{"id":"6c7aa8b8-31c6-4195-bdef-f98307f8ee3d","title":"云生慈摇摇头：“不必。我前来，本就是为了解决此事。事情并非因","content":"云生慈摇摇头：“不必。我前来，本就是为了解决此事。事情并非因你们而起，你们一心想着凡间，还收留了常佑，我要感谢你们才是。怎么好收下你们的东西。”","parentId":null,"children":[],"createdAt":1780917485623},"bookId":"3ef2c972-dba1-4872-8b43-3b40b0f05f0c","deletedAt":1780917494529},{"id":"bca795af-787c-4a4b-b623-00d04319381f","type":"mindMapCard","item":{"id":"5de21141-1ff1-42ab-9f38-9e5d12adad6e","title":"常佑就着那个手抓着手的姿势，迈了一大步。她越过云生慈，把原镜","content":"常佑就着那个手抓着手的姿势，迈了一大步。她越过云生慈，把原镜拿了过来，收进自己的兜里。","parentId":null,"children":[],"createdAt":1780917485623},"bookId":"3ef2c972-dba1-4872-8b43-3b40b0f05f0c","deletedAt":1780917494529},{"id":"c503f267-07ef-4e46-9734-182645edfb8a","type":"mindMapCard","item":{"id":"ab3ef203-0360-4ef1-acf4-ee1093bc874b","title":"云生慈看着她，她不服气似的看了回去。","content":"云生慈看着她，她不服气似的看了回去。","parentId":null,"children":[],"createdAt":1780917485623},"bookId":"3ef2c972-dba1-4872-8b43-3b40b0f05f0c","deletedAt":1780917494529},{"id":"348a41cd-7aaa-402b-aad4-4d404c60d1e1","type":"mindMapCard","item":{"id":"af3c3a9a-0f87-40ce-8bd1-f13fe7fe3579","title":"“还给他。”","content":"“还给他。”","parentId":null,"children":[],"createdAt":1780917485623},"bookId":"3ef2c972-dba1-4872-8b43-3b40b0f05f0c","deletedAt":1780917494529},{"id":"9661d854-755d-4918-a2a2-fda35f1d96ff","type":"mindMapCard","item":{"id":"48f62312-9a1f-43e9-8f32-b71dc7670a03","title":"“说不定有用呢！”","content":"“说不定有用呢！”","parentId":null,"children":[],"createdAt":1780917485623},"bookId":"3ef2c972-dba1-4872-8b43-3b40b0f05f0c","deletedAt":1780917494529},{"id":"930cf7fc-5248-46ae-9638-e0b02b8389ec","type":"mindMapCard","item":{"id":"5bebcb89-69a2-491a-ae1d-fa6b093037be","title":"“不是给你的。”","content":"“不是给你的。”","parentId":null,"children":[],"createdAt":1780917485623},"bookId":"3ef2c972-dba1-4872-8b43-3b40b0f05f0c","deletedAt":1780917494529},{"id":"61ddf058-734b-4d46-b2ff-9ea1547cc917","type":"mindMapCard","item":{"id":"2ea5fa1e-6816-490f-806a-9cae61445de4","title":"“我帮你收下了。”","content":"“我帮你收下了。”","parentId":null,"children":[],"createdAt":1780917485623},"bookId":"3ef2c972-dba1-4872-8b43-3b40b0f05f0c","deletedAt":1780917494530},{"id":"9fe8485f-fa51-4ffb-ba2c-2a3c3b0d992b","type":"mindMapCard","item":{"id":"43554460-a60c-4e8e-9ea4-18f68efcc1c5","title":"“你的脾气在这也改不过来吗？”","content":"“你的脾气在这也改不过来吗？”","parentId":null,"children":[],"createdAt":1780917485623},"bookId":"3ef2c972-dba1-4872-8b43-3b40b0f05f0c","deletedAt":1780917494530},{"id":"c204af83-f940-40db-8d9c-4d2beeb83cc5","type":"mindMapCard","item":{"id":"7c8b5c20-d22a-45de-ba4e-d8124d32f101","title":"“怎样，你要打吗？”","content":"“怎样，你要打吗？”","parentId":null,"children":[],"createdAt":1780917485623},"bookId":"3ef2c972-dba1-4872-8b43-3b40b0f05f0c","deletedAt":1780917494530},{"id":"b2f932f4-91e0-44b6-8a6f-7674d21b6bec","type":"mindMapCard","item":{"id":"639cfd97-b71d-4052-940e-f4708e0e08fc","title":"常佑做了个鬼脸，吐着舌头翻白眼，她笃定云生慈现在肯定不会开打","content":"常佑做了个鬼脸，吐着舌头翻白眼，她笃定云生慈现在肯定不会开打，下面还有事要办呢，这木头肯定会先处理更要紧的，再想办法和自己打一架——她倒是巴不得打一架呢！这厮把门一关，可把自己难受死了。云生慈气极反笑，干脆放开了抓她的手，转过身去，开始测算方位。准备下界。","parentId":null,"children":[],"createdAt":1780917485623},"bookId":"3ef2c972-dba1-4872-8b43-3b40b0f05f0c","deletedAt":1780917494530},{"id":"3ec8992f-5744-4e4e-a7eb-e77b5aa95f66","type":"mindMapCard","item":{"id":"037405e7-062b-4249-811c-8a5dc79af5a7","title":"林九霄眨眨眼睛，哇，这就是爱情的力量吧。刚刚还严肃的不得了的","content":"林九霄眨眨眼睛，哇，这就是爱情的力量吧。刚刚还严肃的不得了的云生慈，只要扭头面对常佑就换了一种表情。他居然从这火药味十足的对话当中，尝到了一丝诡异的甜蜜。","parentId":null,"children":[],"createdAt":1780917485623},"bookId":"3ef2c972-dba1-4872-8b43-3b40b0f05f0c","deletedAt":1780917494530},{"id":"a0363576-10d0-4c13-8790-3834cee25732","type":"mindMapCard","item":{"id":"1db7a5aa-8e99-427c-9f5f-d5698299397b","title":"李继的和事佬人格重新上线：“两位前辈...”","content":"李继的和事佬人格重新上线：“两位前辈...”","parentId":null,"children":[],"createdAt":1780917485623},"bookId":"3ef2c972-dba1-4872-8b43-3b40b0f05f0c","deletedAt":1780917494530},{"id":"02c8cbe1-ba8b-44e7-898c-f779593c7a0b","type":"mindMapCard","item":{"id":"2796555b-4d69-46bc-8c90-533341dfac8f","title":"二人同时扭头看他：“干嘛？”","content":"二人同时扭头看他：“干嘛？”","parentId":null,"children":[],"createdAt":1780917485623},"bookId":"3ef2c972-dba1-4872-8b43-3b40b0f05f0c","deletedAt":1780917494530},{"id":"0b7c1fe4-3e7e-464e-8c9b-787d1e43fba9","type":"mindMapCard","item":{"id":"6153eb33-4923-40bc-a69a-afff0fadae8f","title":"异口同声。","content":"异口同声。","parentId":null,"children":[],"createdAt":1780917485623},"bookId":"3ef2c972-dba1-4872-8b43-3b40b0f05f0c","deletedAt":1780917494530